for writing code for db contoller
  ->first write the const query
  ->then extract the values from the data
  ->then write try catch block
  ->then log the attempt message
  ->then query the database
  ->see if the data is retured or not
  ->then log the success message
  ->else log the error message
  ->if inserting data then check for unique constraint violation
  ->if updating data then check for unique constraint violation
  ->if deleting data then check for foreign key constraint violation
  ->then write the return statement 

